  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Our client is a market leaders for Industrial Distribution and Supply Chain Solution. Due to their current expansion plan, they are looking for Warehouse Assistant to join their team, in hopes of developing the current high performing team. They are located at East.</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in daily warehouse operations to ensure smooth workflow.</li>\n  <li>Receive, check quantity &amp; quality, and sort incoming goods (parts and supplies).</li>\n  <li>Store items neatly and accessibly in the warehouse.</li>\n  <li>Pick and pack items for delivery based on requests.</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate records of inventory and stock locations.</li>\n  <li>Handle returned goods and update relevant departments.</li>\n  <li>Keep warehouse clean, safe, and organized at all times.</li>\n  <li>Support stock-taking and general warehouse tasks.</li>\n  <li>Work with suppliers and forwarders to arrange shipments.</li>\n  <li>Prepare shipping/freight-forwarding documentation.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Possess Forklift License</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested candidates who wish to apply for the advertised position, please click APPLY NOW or email an updated copy of your resume/cv.</p>\n<p>We regret that only shortlisted candidate will be notified.</p>\n<p>Email: <strong>jobs@recruitpedia.sg</strong></p>\n<p>Recruitpedia Pte. Ltd.</p>\n<p>EA License No. 19C9682</p>\n<p>EA Reg. No. R23115141 (Tan Su Yee)</p>",
